'''热带风暴妮科尔'''（{{lang|en|Tropical Storm Nicole}}）是[[2010年大西洋飓风季|2010年大西洋飓风季]]第十六个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]和第十四场获命名的风暴，也是这年九月形成的第八场热带风暴（数量之多创下新纪录）<ref>{{cite report | last1 = Kimberlain | first1 = Todd | last2 = Blake | first2 = Eric | last3 = Brennan | first3 = Michael | date = 2010-10-01 | title = Monthly Tropical Weather Summary: September 2010 | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160314093117/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/tws/MIATWSAT_sep.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/tws/MIATWSAT_sep.shtml? | series = Tropical Cyclone Monthly Summary | deadurl = no | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] }}</ref>。气旋持续时间很短，结构也异常不对称，但依然在[[牙买加|牙买加]]降下暴雨并引发大面积洪灾。系统源自大规模[[季风槽|季风低气压区]]，于9月28日在[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西北部发展成热带低气压。气旋向东北方向移动，结构很不寻常，[[大气环流|环流]]杂乱无章，中心附近的[[雷暴|雷暴]]很少。妮科尔以弱热带风暴强度逼近[[古巴|古巴]]海岸，于9月29日在该国上空失去热带天气系统特征。风暴残留进入[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]上空，最终被另一个[[温带气旋|温带天气系统]]吸收。

受异常结构影响，风暴产生的最强雷暴远离中心，大部分天气活动发生在加勒比海中北部上空。妮科尔在牙买加引发大面积停电，超过28.8万居民受到影响。高达940毫米的降水在[[牙买加行政区划|多个区]]引发重大洪灾，有528套房屋不是被毁便是严重受损。牙买加的农田和环境也受到重创，生态环境遭到污染。估计该国一共受到价值2.4亿美元的破坏，另有16人丧生。此外，[[古巴|古巴]]、[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]和[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]发生轻度洪灾，风暴残留还令[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]沿线大气变得更不稳定，又引发更多的破坏和人员伤亡。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Nicole 2010 track.png}}
2010年9月下旬，[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]西北部上空存在多种天气系统共同影响，其中包括[[热带扰动|扰动天气区]]的大规模[[雨带|雨带]]、[[低气压|低气压]]、[[季风槽|季风槽]]和[[2010年热带风暴马修|热带风暴马修]]的残留热带湿气<ref>{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305011406/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2010/TWDAT.201009270000.txt | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2010/TWDAT.201009270000.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2010-09-27 | last = Formosa | first = Mike | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。与此同时，[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦]]海岸沿线上空存在大规模上层[[高压脊|高压脊]]，扰动天气附近高空中的[[变形_(气象学)|分流]]作用为少量[[对流|对流]]的发展提供良好条件<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2010/TWDAT.201009261748.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2010-09-26 | last = Wallice | first = Patricia | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112035/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2010/TWDAT.201009261748.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = TXT | accessdate = 2017-01-01 }}</ref>。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]指出，这片海域的大气环流有利于形成热带天气系统，到9月27日时对流内已形成大规模下层低气压区<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2010/TWDAT.201009271829.txt | title = Tropical Weather Discussion | date = 2010-09-27 | last = Wallice | first = Patricia | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304210439/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWDAT/2010/TWDAT.201009271829.txt | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。次日，低气压区周边的[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]提升到接近热带风暴水平，下层气压也随之稳步下降<ref>{{cite report | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303190857/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009280911/index.php?basin=atl | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009280911/index.php?basin=atl | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2010-09-28 | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。系统发展期间，加勒比海西北部上空一直存在中等强度的西向[[风切变|风切变]]，致使气旋无法形成对称结构<ref name="TCR" />，到9月28日时已发展出长条状的低气压中心，最强风力位于在远离中心的西北象征内<ref>{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009281200/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009281200 | title = Graphical Tropical Weather Outlook | date = 2010-09-28 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Pasch | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303223830/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/gtwo/atl/201009281200/index.php?basin=atl&current_issuance=201009281200 | first = Richard | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。虽然气旋结构不对称，但由于地面和[[气象卫星|卫星观测]]结果都表明深层对流西侧有清晰的环流中心形成，因此美国国家飓风中心还是在[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]当天下午15点开始针对热带低气压发布公告<ref name="disc1">{{cite report |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160526051618/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.001.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.001.shtml? |title=Tropical Depression Sixteen Discussion Number 1 |date=2010-09-28 |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |location=Miami, Florida |work=National Hurricane Center |last=Pasch |first=Richard |accessdate=2017-01-01 |archivedate=2016-05-26 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。不过经过飓风季后的重新分析，气象机构认定三小时前古巴[[青年岛|青年岛]]以南约120公里海域就已形成热带风暴<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL162010_Nicole.pdf | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Nicole | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2011-01-31 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | last = Blake | deadurl = no | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161222073219/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL162010_Nicole.pdf | first = Eric | page = 1–4 | archivedate = 2016-12-22 }}</ref>。

[[File:TS_Nicole_over_Cuba_-_water_vapor_2010-09-29_1415z.png|thumb]]降水最多。]]

受大规模中到上层低压槽和西侧的[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响，妮科尔存在的大部分时间里总体向东北移动<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="disc1" />。风暴成型数小时后，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机发现气旋中心杂乱无章，最强烈的阵风和雷暴位于中心以东约400公里处<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="discuss2">{{cite report | last = Pasch | first = Richard | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312183325/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.002.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.002.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Sixteen Discussion Number 2 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-09-28 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2016-03-12 }}</ref>。相比之下，风暴中心风力很小，对流零散，结构类似北印度洋的[[季风槽|季风低气压]]<ref name="discuss2" /><ref name="discuss3">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.003.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Sixteen Discussion Number 3 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Beven | first = Jack | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312144342/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.003.shtml | archivedate = 2016-03-12 }}</ref>。这种混乱的结构导致气象学家对气旋分类存在分歧，美国国家飓风中心认为系统属热带气旋，古巴气象学家何塞·鲁别拉（{{lang|en|José Rubiera}}）则认为该国附近没有强劲风力，所以上空或附近都“不存在热带风暴”<ref>{{cite news | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-09-30 | website = Cuba Encuentro | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925125936/http://www.cubaencuentro.com/cuba/noticias/desacuerdo-sobre-la-tormenta-nicole-entre-cuba-y-estados-unidos-245946 | title = Desacuerdo sobre la tormenta Nicole entre Cuba y Estados Unidos | url = http://www.cubaencuentro.com/cuba/noticias/desacuerdo-sobre-la-tormenta-nicole-entre-cuba-y-estados-unidos-245946 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-09-25 }}</ref>。

9月29日，[[气象雷达|雷达数据]]表明气旋北半部上空的对流逐渐增多<ref>{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312125458/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.004.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Sixteen Discussion Number 4 | accessdate = 2011-01-09 | date = 2010-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Stewart | first = Stacy | archivedate = 2016-03-12 }}</ref>，南半部的强烈[[雨带|雷暴带]]也向中心聚拢，多个[[气象浮标|气象浮标]]和多艘[[气象观测船|气象观测船]]测得热带风暴强度持续风速<ref name="discuss5" />。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}中午12点左右，妮科尔在古巴以南近海达到风力时速75公里、最低[[气压|气压]]995[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.38[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度<ref name="TCR" />。但是，气旋强度虽有提升<ref name="discuss5">{{cite report | first1 = Daniel | last2 = Pasch | first2 = Richard | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313014715/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.005.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Number 5 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-09-29 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | last1 = Brown | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-13 }}</ref>，环流却很快就变得极其细长，在古巴上空已无法追踪，美国国家飓风中心为此宣布风暴到{{lang|en|UTC}}下午15点时已不属热带气旋<ref name="TCR" /><ref>{{cite report | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.006.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Discussion Number 6 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Brown | first = Daniel | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312163110/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.discus.006.shtml | date = 2010-09-29 }}</ref>。残留的低气压区开始同附近的低压槽相互影响，在美国东南沿海地区产生可观降水。此外，妮科尔尚属热带气旋时就是在这条低压槽的影响下移动。系统加速向东北前进，逐渐呈现出[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统特征]]，于{{lang|en|UTC}}9月30日早上6点在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]上空转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，再于12小时后同[[北卡罗莱纳州|北卡罗莱纳州]]东部上空尚在发展的天气系统逐渐融合。<ref name="TCR" />受妮科尔影响，加勒比地区中北部上空持续存在低气压和大规模旋转气流，促使[[2010年飓风保拉|飓风保拉]]在10月初发展形成<ref name="PaulaTCR">{{cite report | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161222070320/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL182010_Paula.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL182010_Paula.pdf | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Hurricane Paula | first = Robbie J. | last = Berg | date = 2010-12-20 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | page = 1 | archivedate = 2016-12-22 }}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==

=== 加勒比地区 ===
面对可能来袭的热带风暴，[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]、巴哈马西北部和中部、古巴[[马坦萨斯省|马坦萨斯省]]、[[西恩富戈斯省|西恩富戈斯省]]、[[比亚克拉拉省|比亚克拉拉省]]、[[圣斯皮里图斯省|圣斯皮里图斯省]]和[[谢戈德阿维拉省|谢戈德阿维拉省]]于9月28日收到[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]<ref name="pub001">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.public.001.shtml? | title = Tropical Depression Sixteen Advisory Number 1 | accessdate = 2010-09-28 | year = 2010 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160311153348/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.public.001.shtml | deadurl = no | location = Miami, Florida | work = National Hurricane Center | last = Pasch | first = Richard | type = Advisory | archivedate = 2016-03-11 | date =  }}</ref>。但次日报导表明风暴消散后，上述警告中止生效<ref name="public005">{{cite report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.public.006.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Advisory Number 6 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | year = 2010 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | last1 = Brown | first1 = Daniel | location = Miami, Florida | last2 = Pasch | first2 = Richard | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312135932/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.public.006.shtml | type = Advisory | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | deadurl = no | date =  }}</ref>。气象学家发出警告，称开曼群岛各地天气可能会非常恶劣，群岛低洼地区的学校和政府机构暂时关闭<ref name="compass">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160325003122/http://compasscayman.com/caycompass/2010/09/29/weather-causes-flight-cancellations/ | url = https://www.caymancompass.com/2010/09/29/Weather-causes-flight-cancellations/ | title = Weather causes flight cancellations | date = 2010-09-29 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | newspaper = Cayman Compass | last = Shooman | first = Joe | deadurl = no }}</ref>，应急工作组疏通风暴排水渠的淤塞，并准备好多个避难所<ref name="Cayman">{{cite report |url=http://www.gov.ky/portal/page/portal/hmchome/pressroom/2010/lookingback |title=Looking back at the 2010 Hurricane Season |date=2010-12-03 |accessdate=2017-01-01 |type=Press release |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928043133/http://www.gov.ky/portal/page?_pageid=3701%2C6816985&_dad=portal&_schema=portal |work=Cayman Prepared |publisher=Hazard Management Cayman Islands |archivedate=2015-09-28 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。[[大开曼|大开曼]]出现雷暴，迫使[[开曼航空|开曼航空]]（{{lang|en|Cayman Airways}}）取消10月29日飞往[[开曼布拉克|开曼布拉克]]和[[小开曼|小开曼]]的所有快运航班，同时向滞留旅客提供能够耐受恶劣天气的喷气航班服务<ref name="compass" />。此外，恶劣海况还迫使开曼群岛全部三个岛屿发布海洋警告<ref name="Caymans">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160402000523/http://compasscayman.com/caycompass/2010/09/29/cyclone-floods-cayman/ | url = https://www.caymancompass.com/2010/09/29/Cyclone-floods-Cayman/ | title = Cyclone floods Cayman | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-09-29 | newspaper = Cayman Compass | last = Markoff | archivedate = 2016-04-02 | first = Alan }}</ref><ref name="herald">{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Nicole forms, may skirt Florida | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | publisher = CBS News | date = 2010-09-29 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150926012015/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-nicole-forms-may-skirt-florida/ | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-nicole-forms-may-skirt-florida/ | archivedate = 2015-09-26 }}</ref>。

[[牙买加|牙买加]]的[[山洪警报|山洪警报]]持续生效四天之久，直到10月3日才中止<ref name="flashflood">{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115121/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Flash-Flood-Warning-extended-for-Jamaica |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Flash-Flood-Warning-extended-for-Jamaica |title=Flash flood warning extended for Jamaica |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |date=2010-09-29 |accessdate=2017-01-01 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Flash-flood-warning-lifted | title = Flash flood warning lifted | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-10-03 | newspaper = Jamaica Observer | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303203958/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Flash-flood-warning-lifted | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。9月29至30日，岛上准备应对气旋可能带来的暴雨，许多学校、企业，以及位于[[京斯敦|京斯敦]]的美国大使馆临时关闭<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Schools-closed-until-further-notice |title=Schools closed until further notice |date=2010-09-29 |accessdate=2017-01-01 |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115511/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Schools-closed-until-further-notice |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/US-Embassy-closed |title=US Embassy closed due to Nicole |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |date=2010-09-30 |accessdate=2017-01-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304204627/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/US-Embassy-closed |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。9月29日晚，全岛公共交通中断<ref>{{cite news |accessdate=2017-01-01 |date=2010-09-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150928011534/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/JUTC-buses-to-stop-at-9-30-tonight |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/JUTC-buses-to-stop-at-9-30-tonight |title=JUTC buses to stop at 9:30 tonight |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |archivedate=2015-09-28 }}</ref>，船主接到警告，建议他们固定好船只<ref name="flashflood" />。风暴期间，警察和军队在岛上巡逻，随时准备应对各种紧急情况<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304135553/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Army--police-fully-mobilised---Golding |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Army--police-fully-mobilised---Golding |title=Army, police fully mobilized |date=2010-09-29 |accessdate=2017-01-01 |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |archivedate=2016-03-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

