=== 美国 ===
9月28日，气象部门向[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]、[[佛罗里达湾|佛罗里达湾]]和佛罗里达州[[朱庇特_(佛罗里达州)|朱庇特]]沿海以南地区发布热带风暴警告。朱庇特水湾以北至[[布里瓦德县_(佛罗里达州)|布里瓦德县]][[赛巴斯蒂安港|赛巴斯蒂安港]]（{{lang|en|Sebastian Inlet}}）间地区和东沙布耳角（{{lang|en|East Cape Sable}}）以北至[[柯里尔县|柯里尔县]][[乔科洛斯基_(佛罗里达州)|乔科洛斯基]]（{{lang|en|Chokoloskee}}）接获热带风暴观察预警。<ref name="pub001" />次日气象机构认为妮科尔已不大可能直接袭击佛罗里达州，所以上述警告和观察预警停止生效<ref name="pub005">{{cite report | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312182523/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.public.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2010/al16/al162010.public.005.shtml? | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Advisory Number 5 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-09-29 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | last1 = Brown | first1 = Daniel | last2 = Pasch | first2 = Richard | type = Advisory | archivedate = 2016-03-12 }}</ref>。不过，[[棕榈滩县|棕榈滩县]]、[[布劳沃德县|布劳沃德县]]、[[迈阿密-戴德县|迈阿密-戴德县]]、柯里尔县和[[门罗县_(佛罗里达州)|门罗县]]的洪灾观察预警依然有效，直至9月30日止<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = ChipleyPaper | title = Tropical Depression 16 update | date = 2010-09-28 | accessdate = 2012-03-13 | url = http://www.chipleypaper.com/news/tropical-7280-depression-hurricane.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120313051819/http://www.chipleypaper.com/news/tropical-7280-depression-hurricane.html | archivedate = 2012-03-13 }}</ref>。

9月28日，[[奥兰多国际机场|奥兰多国际机场]]和[[奥兰多行政机场|行政机场]]接到机场天气警告，抵达的航班暂时不能降落，要求飞机员只要可能就改飞其他机场。[[西南航空|西南航空]]的八架班机转飞到[[坦帕_(佛罗里达州)|坦帕]]和[[杰克逊维尔_(佛罗里达州)|杰克逊维尔]]的机场，[[捷蓝航空|捷蓝航空]]也有一架航班改飞[[棕榈滩国际机场|西棕榈滩]]。机场官员之后宣布运作恢复正常，<ref>{{cite news | title = Rain and wet weather create dangerous driving and travel conditions | date = 2010-09-29 | url = http://www.cfnews13.com/article/news/2010/september/155920/Tropical-Depression-Sixteen-causes-dangerous-driving-conditions | archivedate = 2012-02-29 | publisher = Central Florida News 13 | accessdate = 2015-09-24 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120229114241/http://www.cfnews13.com/article/news/2010/september/155920/Tropical-Depression-Sixteen-causes-dangerous-driving-conditions }}</ref>但[[迈亚密国际机场|迈亚密国际机场]]次日又有26架次航班取消<ref>{{cite news | title = TS Nicole cancels flights in and out of MIA | date = 2010-09-30 | publisher = WSVN 7 News | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | accessdate = 2013-11-11 | url = http://www.wsvn.com/news/articles/local/21002347220452/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111094308/http://www.wsvn.com/news/articles/local/21002347220452/ }}</ref>。

9月29日，北卡罗莱纳州[[不伦瑞克县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|不伦瑞克县]]和[[新汉诺威县|新汉诺威县]]官员准备好多个避难所，容留那些无法返回家园的灾民。次日，妮科尔虽已转变成温带气旋，但后续的天气系统又令天气进一步恶化，新汉诺威县和[[彭德县_(北卡罗莱纳州)|彭德县]]多所学校依然停课。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://capefearbusiness.com/?p=5521 | title = Tropical Storm Nicole takes aim at the Cape Fear region | accessdate = 2013-11-11 | date = 2010-09-29 | work = Cape Fear Business News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111094210/http://capefearbusiness.com/?p=5521 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2013-11-11 }}</ref>9月30日至10月1日，面对长时间降雨的威胁，[[马里兰州|马里兰州]][[肯特县_(马里兰州)|肯特县]]收到洪灾观察预警。9月30日，[[美国国家气象局|美国国家气象局]]还向当地发布[[烈风警告|大风公告]]和[[沿海洪灾公告|沿海洪灾公告]]。<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.doverpost.com/article/20100929/NEWS/309299999 | newspaper = The Dover Post | title = Delmarva Power prepares for Tropical Storm Nicole | date = 2010-09-29 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322003606/http://www.doverpost.com/article/20100929/NEWS/309299999 | archivedate = 2016-03-22 }}</ref>

== 影响 ==

=== 牙买加 ===
[[File:Nicole_sept_29_2010_1745Z.jpg|thumb]]

受风暴及其扰动天气前身的共同影响，牙买加大部分地区的降水持续数天之久，9月26至30日间，[[威斯特摩兰区_(牙买加)|威斯特摩兰区]]的贝莱索（{{lang|en|Belleisle}}）降雨总量高达940毫米，为全岛最高<ref name="TCR" />。其他各区这几天的降雨量大多在300毫米以上。如此充沛的降水在当地属30年一遇水平，多地雨量达到九月平均降雨量的三倍。岛上大部分区域的风速不强，但强烈的对流带还催生出三股[[微下击暴流|微下击暴流]]。<ref name="report">{{cite report | publisher = Planning Institute of Jamaica | date = 2010-11 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304000535/http://www.pioj.gov.jm/Portals/0/Sustainable_Development/Tropical%20Storm%20Nicole_Impact%20Assessment_Final.pdf | title = Tropical Storm Nicole Impact Assessment | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.pioj.gov.jm/Portals/0/Sustainable_Development/Tropical%20Storm%20Nicole_Impact%20Assessment_Final.pdf }}</ref>数十条河流阻塞，导致多起[[山崩|山体滑坡]]，许多社区洪水泛滥，并以牙买加南部各区受灾最为严重<ref name="report" /><ref name="bulletin">{{cite report | type = Information bulletin | publisher = [[红十字会与红新月会国际联合会|International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies]] | date = 2010-10-01 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/4F6FF515C48C4B7B492577AF00828AEF-Full_Report.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304075336/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/4F6FF515C48C4B7B492577AF00828AEF-Full_Report.pdf | title = Jamaica: Tropical Storm Nicole – Information bulletin n° 1 | work = ReliefWeb | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。

[[File:Fatal_Landslide.jpg|thumb]]一座棚屋倒塌，屋内三名建筑工人遇难。]]

牙买加共有50万7831人受灾，导致16人死亡（其中14人已经确认），42人受伤<ref name="report" />。[[圣安德鲁区_(牙买加)|圣安德鲁区]]的桑迪园（{{lang|en|Sandy Park}}）有套靠近街道[[沟壑|沟壑]]的房屋在气旋来袭期间坍塌，事后人们在附近找到五具尸体，另外失踪的一人推定也已死亡<ref name="confirm">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303184404/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Remembering-the-Sandy-Park-six_8025119 | url = http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Remembering-the-Sandy-Park-six_8025119 | title = Remembering the Sandy Park six | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | date = 2010-10-05 | newspaper = Jamaica Observer | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20101013/lead/lead5.html | title = Sandy Gully deaths could have been prevented – NWA | date = 2010-10-13 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | newspaper = The Gleaner | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928000654/http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20101013/lead/lead5.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-09-28 }}</ref>。圣安德鲁区还有一幢棚屋倒塌，正在屋内休息的三名建筑工人丧生<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055957/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Three-men-crushed-to-death-in-Norbrook-shack |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Three-men-crushed-to-death-in-Norbrook-shack |title=Three crushed to death in Norbrook shack |accessdate=2017-01-01 |date=2010-09-30 |last=Robinson |first=Corey |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。[[圣凯瑟琳区|圣凯瑟琳区]]有一名少女被倒塌的板房砸死<ref>{{cite news |date=2010-09-30 |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Tree-crushes-little-girl-to-death |title=Tree crushes little girl to death |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041351/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Tree-crushes-little-girl-to-death |deadurl=yes |accessdate=2017-01-01 |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。岛上各地共有三人在被洪水卷走后溺毙<ref name="toll">{{cite news | url = http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20101002/lead/lead1.html | title = More bodies – Nicole casualties climb death toll: 13 | date = 2010-10-02 | newspaper = The Gleaner | last = Hall | first = Arthur | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150929010306/http://jamaica-gleaner.com/gleaner/20101002/lead/lead1.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archivedate = 2015-09-29 }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |date=2010-09-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304003202/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Nicole-pains_8008910 |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Nicole-pains_8008910 |title=Nicole pains – 2 dead, 6 missing as storm ravages |accessdate=2017-01-01 |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。微下击暴流在威斯特摩兰区首府[[滨海萨凡纳|滨海萨凡纳]]催生出[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]，将多幢建筑的屋顶撕开，致使五人需要住院治疗<ref name="report" /><ref>{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Nicole quickly losing steam | date = 2010-09-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20101002020302/http://www2.tbo.com/content/2010/sep/29/291806/tropical-depression-aims-at-cuba-then-florida/weather-hurricane/ | archivedate = 2010-10-02 | newspaper = The Tampa Tribune | accessdate = 2015-09-24 | url = http://www2.tbo.com/content/2010/sep/29/291806/tropical-depression-aims-at-cuba-then-florida/weather-hurricane/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。气旋过去后，人们在圣凯瑟琳区路边的废墟中找到一具遗体<ref>{{cite news |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220731/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/latestnews/Body-found-on-Ewarton-Main-Road |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/latestnews/Body-found-on-Ewarton-Main-Road |title=Body found on Edwarton Main Road |accessdate=2017-01-01 |date=2010-10-03 |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |archivedate=2016-03-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。牙买加七个区都有社区因街道、公路和桥梁被淹而同周边地区的交通中断，还有成百上千的居民被困家中<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303215241/http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Reports-of-islandwide-flooding-and-damage |url=http://www.jamaicaobserver.com/news/Reports-of-islandwide-flooding-and-damage |title=Floods causing damage islandwide |accessdate=2017-01-01 |date=2010-09-29 |newspaper=Jamaica Observer |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref><ref name="dref">{{cite report | url = http://www.ifrc.org/docs/appeals/10/MDRJM002dfr.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304050307/http://www.ifrc.org/docs/appeals/10/MDRJM002dfr.pdf | title = DREF operation final report – Jamaica: Tropical Storm Nicole | number = DREF operation n° MDRJM002 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | publisher = International Federation of Red Cross and Red Crescent Societies | work = Disaster Relief Emergency Fund | date = 2011-06-02 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | page = 2 | deadurl = no | format = PDF }}</ref>。

洪水对牙买加的[[基础设施|基础设施]]构成重大打击，岛上的大部分经济损失都是由此产生。风暴期间，该国至少有28.8万居民因电线杆倒塌和输电线缆中断致使家中停电。全岛一度有超过40%的自来水供应受到影响。<ref name="report" />多条河流和溪流暴涨，导致数十座桥梁经不住河水冲击而完全坍塌。旷日持久的降水令金斯敦的排水沟渠不堪重负，下水道被彻底淹没，随之而来的洪灾导致该市许多道路无法通行。<ref name="usatoday">{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-11-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131111165157/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2010-09-29-tropical-storm-nicole_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/storms/2010-09-29-tropical-storm-nicole_N.htm | title = Tropical Storm Nicole bringing rain to South Florida | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2010-09-29 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 }}</ref>威斯特摩兰区、[[圣伊丽莎白区|圣伊丽莎白区]]和[[汉诺威区|汉诺威区]]的基础设施受创特别严重，全岛共有543条主要道路受到一定程度破坏<ref name="report" />。所有基础设施遭受的破坏价值共计达200亿[[牙买加元|牙买加元]]（2010年牙买加元，相当于同年的2亿3540万美元）<ref name="bill">{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Nicole bill now at $20 billion | url = http://jamaica-gleaner.com/power/23714 | newspaper = Jamaica Observer | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150925123239/http://jamaica-gleaner.com/power/23714 | archivedate = 2015-09-25 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

妮科尔还对大面积房产构成破坏，共有2169套民宅受损，其中474套程度严重，54套已无法修复，损失总额有2亿7430万牙买加元（2010年牙买加元，相当于同年的89万美元），许多被毁的房屋需要重建<ref name="report" />。全岛大部分庄稼和牲口都被洪水冲走，牙买加的农业因此遭受价值约5亿7650万牙买加元（2010年牙买加元，相当于同年的680万美元）的损失，其中包括全季香蕉产量的四成。环境在牙买加的经济和旅游业中占有举足轻重的地位，此次气旋来袭又对该国环境造成显著影响。工业区和污水处理系统的水流溢出，形成[[地表迳流|地表迳流]]并渗入大面积土地，致使沿海地区受到侵蚀、大片土壤遭到污染，受灾地区的生态环境恶化。此外，当地植被也受到轻度破坏，部分树木被连根拔起。<ref name="report" />

=== 其他地区 ===
尚在古巴近海逐渐增强时，妮科尔的外围雨带就在正遭受严重旱灾的该国产生瓢泼大雨<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111128204343/http://alocubano.wordpress.com/2010/09/30/la-tormenta-tropical-que-inventaron-los-medios-segun-rubiera/#more-885 | title = La tormenta tropical que inventaron los medios, según Rubiera | deadurl = no | date = 2010-09-30 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | first = Jorge García | website = Alocubano | archivedate = 2011-11-28 | url = https://alocubano.wordpress.com/2010/09/30/la-tormenta-tropical-que-inventaron-los-medios-segun-rubiera/#more-885 | last = Sosa }}</ref>。从各个地点来看，古巴东南沿海地区降雨量特别高，地处[[格拉玛省|格拉玛省]]山区的克鲁兹角（{{lang|en|Cape Cruz}}）在48小时里共降下235毫米雨量。当地短暂测得[[烈风|烈风]]强度大风，[[关塔那摩湾|关塔那摩湾]]的阵风时速达到85公里。<ref name="TCR" />面对风暴来袭，古巴东部各地共有300人寻求庇护。格拉玛省多条河流泛滥成灾，沿海小镇[[皮隆_(古巴)|皮隆]]有八套房屋坍塌，另有300多幢被淹。洪水还令多条公路阻塞，格拉玛省至通往[[圣地亚哥-德古巴|圣地亚哥-德古巴]]的高速公路有部分路段毁于一旦。受妮科尔影响，古巴损失的农作物和牲畜一共约重2.5[[公吨|吨]]。<ref name="cubaimpact">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112352/http://www.elnuevoherald.com/ultimas-noticias/article2009039.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.elnuevoherald.com/ultimas-noticias/article2009039.html | title = Lluvias causan daños en cultivos y viviendas | agency = Agencia EFE | newspaper = El Nuevo Herald | date = 2010-10-02 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>不过，上述影响总体而言还非常轻微，并且降水还令该国持续已久的旱情得到缓解<ref>{{cite news | deadurl = yes | agency = [[法新社|Agence France-Presse]] | publisher = Noticias 24 | archivedate = 2015-09-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928161202/http://www.noticias24.com/actualidad/noticia/174473/lluvias-de-nicole-incomunican-pequenas-aldeas-y-alivian-sequia-en-cuba/ | date = 2010-09-30 | url = http://www.noticias24.com/actualidad/noticia/174473/lluvias-de-nicole-incomunican-pequenas-aldeas-y-alivian-sequia-en-cuba/ | title = Lluvias de Nicole incomunican pequeñas aldeas y alivian sequía en Cuba | access-date = 2017-01-01 }}</ref>。

[[File:Nicole2010filledrainblk.gif|thumb]]

时速82公里的阵风令开曼群岛海况恶劣，出现2.5至3米的大浪，导致群岛南部和西部海岸受到轻度[[海蚀|侵蚀]]<ref name="Caymanreport">{{cite report | title = Annual Report 2010–2011 | publisher = Hazard Management Cayman Islands | pages = 9, 14 | date = 2011 | accessdate = 2015-09-28 | work = Cayman Prepared | archivedate = 2015-09-28 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150928023051/http://www.caymanprepared.gov.ky/pls/portal/docs/PAGE/HMCHOME/RESOURCES/ANNUALREPORTS/HMCI%20ANNUAL%20REPORT%20%20201011.PDF | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | url = http://www.caymanprepared.gov.ky/pls/portal/docs/PAGE/HMCHOME/RESOURCES/ANNUALREPORTS/HMCI%20ANNUAL%20REPORT%20%20201011.PDF }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.compasscayman.com/story.aspx?id=35121 | title = Rain to continue | first = Allen | last = Markoff | date = 2010-09-30 | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | newspaper = Cayman Compass | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084512/http://www.compasscayman.com/story.aspx?id=35121 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。群岛大面积区域降下暴雨，其中大开曼降水最多，[[欧文·罗伯茨国际机场|欧文·罗伯茨国际机场]]在前后两天里测得229毫米雨量<ref name="Caymanreport" />。气旋令低洼地区被淹，部分房屋的屋顶漏水，大开曼东部部分地区停电，但群岛整体遭受的破坏程度很轻<ref name="Caymanreport" />。

佛罗里达州虽然一度受到强烈雷暴和阵风的威胁，但之后幸而没有直接受到妮科尔的影响。该州仅降下小雨，<ref>{{cite news | last1 = Kaye | first1 = Ken | last2 = Nolin | first2 = Robert | date = 2010-09-30 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054625/http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2010-09-30/news/sfl-tropical-storm-nicole_1_strongest-winds-and-rain-tropical-storm-nicole-hurricane-center | newspaper = Sun Sentinel | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://articles.sun-sentinel.com/2010-09-30/news/sfl-tropical-storm-nicole_1_strongest-winds-and-rain-tropical-storm-nicole-hurricane-center | title = Short-lived Tropical Storm Nicole no big deal for South Florida | deadurl = no }}</ref>虽然门罗县[[北基拉戈岛|北基拉戈岛]]（{{lang|en|North Key Largo}}）的降雨总量高达323毫米，但[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]大陆远远不及<ref>{{cite book | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | at = section [http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/nicole2010.html Tropical Storm Nicole – 28–29, 2010] | date = 2010-05-10 | first = David | last = Roth | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140721033709/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/nicole2010.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-07-21 }}</ref>。[[迈阿密海滩|迈阿密海滩]]和[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]北部发生街道洪灾，但只有一户民居受损<ref name="TCR" />。巴哈马部分地区也有类似的恶劣天气，但同样没有造成重大后果<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="Nasa">{{cite report | url = https://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2010/h2010_Nicole.html | title = Hurricane Season 2010: Tropical Storm Nicole (Atlantic Ocean) | date = 2010-10-04 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305220401/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/hurricanes/archives/2010/h2010_Nicole.html | publisher = [[美国国家航空航天局|NASA]] | work = Hurricanes/Tropical Cyclones | first = Rob | last = Gutro | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。

=== 风暴转变成温带气旋后 ===
妮科尔的温带残留依然保有充足水分，最终同大规模低气压系统融合并缓慢沿[[美国东岸|美国东岸]]北上<ref name="Nasa" />，由此产生的扰动天气令东岸所有沿海地区及部分内陆地区暴雨倾盆并伴有强烈雷暴，影响范围向北一直延伸到加拿大境内，导致大面积停电<ref name="ctvnews">{{cite news | accessdate = 2012-01-19 | publisher = CTV News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120119043810/http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20101001/Storm-Heads-North-101001/ | url = http://www.ctv.ca/CTVNews/TopStories/20101001/Storm-Heads-North-101001/ | title = Storm kills two in Quebec after flooding U.S. Cities | date = 2010-10-01 | agency = Associated Press | archivedate = 2012-01-19 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，还在各地刷新多项降水纪录<ref name="Nasa" /><ref name="wpc">{{cite report | date = 2010-10-02 | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | title = Heavy Rains Across the Mid-Atlantic and Northeast: September 29–October 2, 2010 | first = Rich | last = Otto | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/winter_storm_summaries/event_reviews/2010/Mid-Atlantic_and_Northeast_Heavy_Rains_2010.pdf | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304131416/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/winter_storm_summaries/event_reviews/2010/Mid-Atlantic_and_Northeast_Heavy_Rains_2010.pdf }}</ref>。[[北卡罗莱纳|北卡罗莱纳]]及周边的天气最为恶劣，9月24日至10月1日这一周里，大部分社区的降雨总量都有200至250毫米<ref name="Nasa" />。[[威尔明顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|威尔明顿]]测得573毫米雨量，创下1871 年后的五天降雨量新纪录，[[金斯顿_(北卡罗莱纳州)|金斯顿]]在此期间也降下380毫米雨量。暴雨引发大面积洪灾，多条河流和溪流的泛滥更令灾情雪上加霜，许多民居被洪水团团围困。<ref name="NC">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2012-09-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.newsobserver.com/2010/10/02/714976/flooding-swamps-counties-down.html | date = 2010-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120930182703/http://www.newsobserver.com/2010/10/02/714976/flooding-swamps-counties-down.html | archivedate = 2012-09-30 | newspaper = The News & Observer | title = Flooding swamps counties Down East }}</ref>由于路况危险，约有150条公路封闭，全州各地发生多起交通事故，共夺走七条人命<ref name="CSM">{{cite news | date = 2010-10-01 | first = Ron | last = Scherer | newspaper = The Christian Science Monitor | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231615/http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/2010/1001/Remnants-of-tropical-storm-Nicole-wallop-East-Coast-with-huge-rainfall | title = Remnants of tropical storm Nicole wallop East Coast with huge rainfall | url = http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/2010/1001/Remnants-of-tropical-storm-Nicole-wallop-East-Coast-with-huge-rainfall | accessdate = 2017-01-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。

